perl-Text-Hyphen: perl-Text-Hyphen (hyphenate words in text)
perl-Text-Hyphen:
perl-Text-Hyphen: Text::Hyphen module is the implementation of the famous Knuth-Liang
perl-Text-Hyphen: algorithm to hyphenate words in text. That means using this module
perl-Text-Hyphen: you can determine positions inside words where it is possible to
perl-Text-Hyphen: insert a hyphen to break a line of text.
perl-Text-Hyphen:
